# A yellowish [[tropical]] [[fruit]] (''[[psidium guajava]]'') often made into [[jam]]s and [[jelly|jellies]]. The [[guava]] fruit is 1¼ to 2 inches, [[globular]] or [[pear]]-shaped with thin, yellow, green, or brown [[skin]]; the [[meat]] is yellowish or pale green to pink in color.
# A tropical [[tree]] which produces such fruit.

